Exhibitions

If you would like a studio visit to view her current paintings, please contact her on 01363 866351 or 07891295672 or email footlightkat@aol.com.

On Friday 25th September 2011 Katharine gave a live interview on her life and work on Radio Devon with Richard Green.

In November 2011, Katharine featured on BBC’s Flog It! “It was a fantastic day, I gave presenter Paul Martin a painting lesson at beautiful Bovey Castle, Dartmoor. So many people contacted me to say how they loved the programme, so thank you Paul for that wonderful opportunity.”
